column2: SELECT d.dr7ObjID, s.plate, s.fiberid, s.mjd, s.ra, s.dec, g.fuv_mag, g.nuv_mag, g.fuv_magErr, g.nuv_magErr, g.e_bv from SpecObj as s into mydb.glx_sdss_dr7_sample JOIN photoobjall as ph on s.bestObjID = ph.objID JOIN specDR7 as d on s.specObjID = d.specObjID JOIN GalexGR6.xSDSSDR7 as x on d.dr7ObjID = x.SDSSobjid JOIN GalexGR6.photoobjall as g on x.objID = g.objID WHERE g.nuv_mag ! = # and x.reverseDistanceRank = # and s.z BETWEEN # AND #
